The '''2020 [[ICF World Junior and U23 Canoe Slalom Championships]]''' will take place in [[Kraków]], [[Poland]] under the auspices of the [[International Canoe Federation]] (ICF) at the [[Kraków-Kolna Canoe Slalom Course]].<ref>{{cite web|title=2020 ICF JUNIOR & U23 CANOE SLALOM WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPS|url=https://www.canoeicf.com/canoe-slalom-world-championships/krakow-2020|website=CanoeICF.com|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref> It will be the 22nd edition of the competition for Juniors (U18) and the 9th edition for the Under 23 category.
