=== Jury === Many prominent singers have served in the jury, including [[Carlo Bergonzi (tenor)|Carlo Bergonzi]], Sir [[Geraint Evans]], [[Marilyn Horne]], [[Gundula Janowitz]], [[Sherrill Milnes]], [[Christoph Prégardien]], Dame [[Joan Sutherland]], Dame [[Anne Evans]], [[René Kollo]], [[Galina Vishnevskaya]] and [[Dame Gwyneth Jones]], Irina Arkhipova and Shen Xiang. There is a separate jury for the "Song Prize", with some members serving on both juries.
On the day between the two competition finals, some of the jury members give master classes to some of the non-finalists, which are open to the public.
